          p WhyAZ’s mission is to share why it’s awesome to live and work in Arizona. We showcase the natural beauty, diverse climate, and vibrant lifestyle we love. Our ultimate goal is to encourage excited, positive people to choose Arizona as a place to grow roots and to contribute to our community.
          p We encourage contribution to the site via an 
            a(href="https://github.com/whyaz/whyaz/#contributing") open source codebase
            | , hosted on GitHub, and solicitation of feedback via a 
